            . I am a pawnbroker, and live with Mr. Neat, in Duke-street, Manchester-square. I produce a gold ring which was pledged at our house on the 15th of January. The youngest prisoner, Harding, pledged it in the name of 
               <persName id="t18160214-64-person732">
                  Ann 
                  Campbell
               <interp inst="t18160214-64-person732" type="surname" value="Campbell"></interp>
